# Function Overloading (Compile Time Polymorphism)

```cpp
class Calculator
{
public:

    int add(int a, int b)
    {
        return a+b;
    }

    double add(double a, double b)
    {
        return a+b;
    }

    int add(int a, int b, int c)
    {
        return a+b+c;
    }
};
```

Compiler decides function at compile time.

